reviewText:
Great unedited footage in top picture quality for the 1965 documentary "A Day in Vietnam" mostly from Tan Son Nhut Air base.
BUT: The second part "Care for casualties" was NOT on the DVD.
Otherwise it would be five stars.

Photo Shows small temple that can be seen in the footage from around TSN Gate # 1 as it looks today
Boring footage, no sound. Pass this one by. Don't waste your time. I need to write four more words, in order to submit.
